      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the caution part but 4000 iu feels so tiny if i'm basically in total darkness for most of the day. i read online that some people do much higher \"loading doses\" to jumpstart their system. if i only do it for like 10 days and then drop back down to a normal dose, isn't that basically fine? it's not like i'm doing it forever.",
